  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, bring 2 cups of water to a boil and add the red lentils, cooking until they are tender.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the vegetable oil over medium heat and saute the chopped onion until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the berbere spice and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cooked fry-grind-rice-khao-khua to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Split the toasted sesame seed burger buns in half and fill with the lentil and rice mixture.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional berbere spice and sesame seeds if desired."
